To actually make transactions with, to buy and sell things with, the fact that its price in US

00:15:27.751 --> 00:15:35.051
dollars or Euros changes so quickly makes it very hard to use as a way of buying and selling stuff.

00:15:36.231 --> 00:15:40.751
To give you a working example, if you are a pizza restaurant that

00:15:40.901 --> 00:15:45.931
accepts payment in bitcoin, I might call up and ask for two pizzas.

