that it cannot ever be used as a true medium of exchange.

00:20:30.462 --> 00:20:36.342
For a currency to be useful as a way of buying and selling stuff that currency’s

00:20:36.652 --> 00:20:42.822
value has to be relatively stable, and bitcoin’s value is far from it.

